      "id": "p2-grammar1",
      "type": "advanced-grammar",
      "title": "DO + YOU + VERB",
      "explanation": "Use do to make simple present questions with you.",
      "details": "Use \"Yes, I do.\" for affirmative short answers and \"No, I don't.\" for negative short answers.",
